but he's come unhinged.

05:39.126 --> 05:41.361
Unhinged is
an understatement,

05:41.395 --> 05:43.129
try murderer...
kidnapper.

05:43.163 --> 05:44.531
No, but in his mind,

05:44.565 --> 05:46.099
