06:08.122 --> 06:09.821
The reason why
he's become unhinged

06:09.856 --> 06:11.323
is because
I rejected him for you.

06:11.358 --> 06:13.559
And he's become
a little obsessed.

06:13.593 --> 06:15.827
Right. And I thought
you were trying to defuse me.

06:15.862 --> 06:17.730
I'm just saying,

06:17.764 --> 06:19.431
I have a certain power over him

06:19.466 --> 06:21.027
